  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and sliced ginger and saute until fragrant.",
    "Add fish sauce, soy sauce, and brown sugar, stirring to combine.",
    "Add pilchards to the saucepan, stirring to coat with the sauce.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in chopped scallions and black pepper.",
    "Continue to simmer for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Serve hot over rice or noodles.",
    "Garnish with additional scallions if desired."
